    "body": "Hm I think it would be better to have it on it's own separate line. The precision in the screenshot is nice and does not abstract anything away. It becomes a bit hard to read like this imo:\r\n\r\n```\r\nEstimated total gas used for script: 500123\r\n\r\nEstimated total cost: 0.234234234234234  ETH (at 10 gwei)\r\n```\r\n\r\nvs:\r\n\r\n```\r\nEstimated gas price: 10 gwei\r\n\r\nEstimated total gas used for script: 500123\r\n\r\nEstimated total cost: 0.234234234234234  ETH\r\n```\r\n\r\nAlso separately, having comma formatting for gas total will also make it easier to read.\r\n\r\n```\r\nEstimated total gas used for script: 6,500,123\r\n```\r\n\r\nvs\r\n\r\n```\r\nEstimated total gas used for script: 6500123\r\n```",
